data.description: Welcome to 1010 43rd 1/2 Avenue NE, Columbia Heights. This splendid 1 1/2 story single family house. Clean exceptionally maintained. Enjoy the Beauty of laminated wood floors in main level. Good size upper level room with walk-in closet. Private fenced backyard quiet and very nice neighborhood easy access to Hwy 65 and 694. 10 minutes to downtown Minneapolis. Couple blocks to nice park. Good schools. Don't miss out on this opportunity to call this amazing house your home sweet home. Schedule a showing right away.
